PMID: 18508509 RSK1 (human) phosphorylation sites: S221, T359, S363, S380, T573, S732 RSK2 (human) phosphorylation sites: S227, T365, S369, S386, T577, S737

PMID: 12150926 PMID: 12150925 PMID: 12408816 Four phosphorylation sites (P-sites) on mTOR have been reported to date (T2446, S2448, S2481 and S1261). However, only S1261 has been described to regulates mTORC1 function (PMID: 19487463). In addition, mTOR autokinase activity (S2481 autophosphorylation) requires S1261 phosphorylation. Therefore, we decided to illustrate mTOR with both the S1261 and S2481 P-sites on this map.
